  <Patch name="Signed Ability Y Value (fdc version)">
    <Description>
	  For damage formulas that use PA + Y, Y can now range from any value from -128 to 127.  To get negative numbers, simply type in the number that is 256 minus the number in question.  For example, if I want damage to be Y to be -2, I type in Y so that Y = 256 - 2 = 254.
          For stat gain / loss formulas that use Y, Y DECREASES stats if Y is less than 128.  If you want Y to increase stats, add 128 to Y.  For example, on the yell formula, if Y = 1, it will reduce your SPD by 1, but if Y = 1 + 128 = 129, it will increase your SPD by 1.  Thus, IF YOU APPLY THIS HACK, YOU WILL NEED TO CHANGE THE DEFAULT VALUES FOR SCREAM, YELL, PREACH...
    </Description>
